{"tid":881230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那新版歷史書刪文革章節，學生表示歡迎","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T13:20:38.000Z","uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a5ffea03f8cddcf277e1811af45660a45a7945","tid":881230,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"【新版教科書刪除「文化大革命」】<br />\n【學生認為可讓錯誤歷史更完美】<br />\n【學者批評模糊政治是非】<br />\n<br />\n新版初中歷史書刪除「文化大革命」的章節，在網上引起激烈的反響。不過一班最受影響的中學生就覺得修改教材是合理的，有人甚至認為會令中國歷史變得更完美。<br />\n<br />\n有學者就批評新版教科書是掩蓋「文革」的錯誤，可能令人日後重蹈覆轍：「這麼大的教訓，白白一筆就抹掉了？如果我們是這樣一個教科書教出來的話，那就可能模糊了政治上的是非，最後可能是重犯歷史的錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n#修改錯誤歷史就可以令歷史變得更完美<br />\n#掩耳盜鈴<br />\n#人類總是犯同樣的錯<br />\n#文化大革命<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1608827989261681/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1608827989261681%2F&d=KTBDpI4eu99qGD55MLZpZtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a57a72bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1608827989261681/</a>"},{"pid":"aec138aeb42c53ecc978812f844f5ad024b81636","tid":881230,"uid":50457,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"唔講就代表無出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585f1875ec15bd6e45bfe59757c97151c5080359","tid":881230,"uid":13914,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"忘記歷史就意味著背叛"},{"pid":"c90415533611326125e27b3506bbd8ffc171b8af","tid":881230,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"大耀進呢"},{"pid":"f70d7ec5526f9a4df7f7fc39721bd7b4e3b9c976","tid":881230,"uid":48735,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"幾個月前嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm